<sect1 id="libwebp" xreflabel="libwebp-&libwebp-version;">
  <?dbhtml filename="libwebp.html"?>

  <title>libwebp-&libwebp-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The libwebp package contains a library and support programs to encode and
      decode images in WebP format.
    </para>

